pan class=usertitle>Sharin's boyfriend<br>Such a sweetheart<br>She loves him SOOOO MUCH!!!</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#000000>(8/15/02 3:32:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fhoggiesreunionfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sipping Some Coffee</span><hr size=1> Wilhelm smiled over at her warmly. His hand rested on hers. It was cold and lifeless. &quot;You were always kind it makes sense you would protect life. All i have done is destroy it anna. You see this ring.&quot; He set it on the table with starlight blue eyes watching it. &quot;That's what they give you for bravery. For foolishness. For condeming men and children to the great beyond. You give trust to easy anna&quot;. Wilhem brought back his hand and rested it by his side. &quot;I am not worthy of it nor of your friendship. For my crimes I will be bound to darkness forever&quot;. Wilhelm frowned looking down. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFF0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/usharinmarr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharin Marr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>All-Mighty Creator of the Board!<br>Bow Down to her<br>She loves Wilhelm!<br>GO WHITES!!!<br>A beautiful and wonderful administrator<br>Would never take away the admin powers of a <br>Promises she won't take away Kerri's powers<br>Unless, that is, she misbehaves<br>Likes to flaunt her powers, but never really uses them</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#000000>(8/17/02 6:10:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fhoggiesreunionfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.freeavatars.net/vpimages/brunettes/fhbl101.gif height=116 width=102></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sipping Some Coffee</span><hr size=1> Anna's eyes were wide, and her mouth went dry. &quot;Wilhelm, that's not at all what you're like!&quot; she said softly. &quot;I don't see why it is that you so easily condemn yourself, but won't condemn others. And also, it was their time to die. Everyone has a time to live, and a time to die. You know that, Wilhelm. It was their time to die. If you hadn't have killed them, someone else would have.<br><br>&quot;I don't give my trust out as easily as you think, Wilhelm,&quot; Anna began earnestly, ignoring the fact that Exilia was digging her claws into her lap. &quot;On my clients, I actually just use a spell so that they think I trust them. With every person, Wilhelm, I only start out with an inkling of trust, and let them build or take away. With patients, I keep the spell until I'm sure I can trust them. With people, I just keep my old opinion until it is built or taken. Wilhelm, you have done nothing to build of the opinion I had of you back in school days. But neither have you done anything to take away from it.&quot;<br><br>One of her slight, slender hand petted the cat Exilia's black fur gently as the other hand scratched under her white chin. Playfully, she saw Wilhelm's hand and pounced pon it. Anna inwardly smiled, knowing that the cat's claws were soft as a feather and as thus could not hurt her friend. <p><b>Okay. Cmon, lets go join Moony now, shall we? Im sure hes feeling quite alone," James said.<br>"In the bathroom?" Sirius said, a look of odd horror on his face.</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCC0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/uwilhelmkruger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wilhelm Kruger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sharin's boyfriend<br>Such a sweetheart<br>She loves him SOOOO MUCH!!!</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#000000>(8/17/02 10:22:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fhoggiesreunionfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sipping Some Coffee</span><hr size=1> Wilhelm looked at the cat. &quot;Tell me anna how many countries have you lost a war for? Failed time and time again? You may believe people have a time and that's a nice philosphy but it does not carry wieght in my world. I saw fathers and brothers as I shot them down anna. Have you ever seen a man's face when he's dying. Screaming for his last breath.  I even killed my own men anna. There was a tank shot. They were in so much pain. They just wanted it to end. So I ended it. I killed even children anna. The french resitance went as young as 10 years old. I found out later what our country had done to the jews. Six million people slaughtered anna, while we were told of relocation camps. Was it there time?  I wish it had been...&quot;  Wilhelm did not finish it with &quot;my time&quot;. She could guess for he knew she was smart. <br><br>Wilhelm sighed at the cat. A look of warmth. Just wanting to hold something , somehow. Just to feel warmth again. Yet wilhelm's hand came back and rested on his side. Wilhelm's eyes held bags now. From nights filled with the screams of victims of war. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fhoggiesreunionfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/pastel/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fhoggiesreunionfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fhoggiesreunionfrm6.threadControl?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/pastel/deleteThread.gif